ass=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/f29e08f9ee088dc4043901f659115d67/0a47e/image-24.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f29e08f9ee088dc4043901f659115d67/8a4e8/image-24.png 150w,\n/static/f29e08f9ee088dc4043901f659115d67/5a46d/image-24.png 300w,\n/static/f29e08f9ee088dc4043901f659115d67/0a47e/image-24.png 600w,\n/static/f29e08f9ee088dc4043901f659115d67/c6d67/image-24.png 734w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>プラグインを有効化すると強制的にログインページの URL が変更されます。\n個人のブログでは問題ないのですが、客先等で共有している場合は変更しない方がいいかもしれません。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2c45b3da15e16796151c7ffdb4242cb5/41be6/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/2c45b3da15e16796151c7ffdb4242cb5/0a47e/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2c45b3da15e16796151c7ffdb4242cb5/8a4e8/5.png 150w,\n/static/2c45b3da15e16796151c7ffdb4242cb5/5a46d/5.png 300w,\n/static/2c45b3da15e16796151c7ffdb4242cb5/0a47e/5.png 600w,\n/static/2c45b3da15e16796151c7ffdb4242cb5/41be6/5.png 638w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>左のメニューから「SiteGuard」→「ログインページ変更」→「ON/OFF」で変更できます。また、このページではログインページの URL も確認できます。</p>\n<p>SiteGuard の詳細設定はこちらが参考になります。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://webst8.com/blog/wordpress-siteguard/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://webst8.com/blog/wordpress-siteguard/</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"通知を消す\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E3%82%92%E6%B6%88%E3%81%99\" aria-label=\"通知を消す permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通知を消す</h4>\n<p>常時表示されているのは気になるので消します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/84d241d7bb285b62c8776073a672bdb9/1c3a5/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/84d241d7bb285b62c8776073a672bdb9/0a47e/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/84d241d7bb285b62c8776073a672bdb9/8a4e8/6.png 150w,\n/static/84d241d7bb285b62c8776073a672bdb9/5a46d/6.png 300w,\n/static/84d241d7bb285b62c8776073a672bdb9/0a47e/6.png 600w,\n/static/84d241d7bb285b62c8776073a672bdb9/1cfc2/6.png 900w,\n/static/84d241d7bb285b62c8776073a672bdb9/1c3a5/6.png 981w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>「DISMISS」と「Yes. enable auto update」を選択すると表示が消えます。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-21","slug":"/64","title":"【WordPress】スパム対策に特化したプラグインを入れてみよう","tags":["wordpress"],"thumbnail":null},"excerpt":"今回入れるプラグインは３つです。 Akismet Anti-Spam Wordfence Security SiteGuard WP Plugin Akismet Anti-Spam WordPress…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#akismet-anti-spam\">Akismet Anti-Spam</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#akismet%E3%81%AE%E3%82%A2%E3%82%AB%E3%82%A6%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88%E3%82%92%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\"><strong>Akismet</strong>のアカウントを設定する</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#your-email-address\">Your Email Address</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#first-name--last-name\">First Name 　/　 Last Name</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#personal-site-url-where-you-will-use-akismet\">Personal Site URL where you will use Akismet:</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EF%BC%93%E3%81%A4%E3%81%AE%E3%83%81%E3%82%A7%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF%E3%83%9C%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF%E3%82%B9\">３つのチェックボックス</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E8%AA%8D%E8%A8%BC%E3%82%B3%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89%E5%85%A5%E5%8A%9B\">認証コード入力</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#wordpress-%E5%81%B4%E3%81%AB-api-key-%E3%82%92%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\">WordPress 側に API KEY を設定</a></p>\n